# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Sizzle & Zesty — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit your actual .env file to git.
#
# Usage:
#   cp .env.example .env
#   Then edit .env with your real keys
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Anthropic API Key — powers the AI features:
#   • "What does this mean?" step explanations
#   • "Oops!" recipe rescue suggestions
#   • Fridge-to-Recipe generation
#   • WhatMeansBtn, OopsBtn, FridgeScreen
#
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
# The app works without this key — AI features will be silently disabled.
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here
